  <summary>Shared libraries provided by freedesktop.org</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      The Freedesktop Platform is a basic runtime for flatpak application
      that contains the most basic libraries and files needed to run
      a linux desktop application. It is based on the yocto distribution
      with the latest version of the freedesktop technologies like
      X11, Mesa, Wayland, dbus, cairo, gstreamer added. It also contains
      SDL2.
    </p>
